text.tspan: Luxembourg land uses based on CORINE Land Cover data. Only showing Forest, Urban, and Water surfaces, with other land uses 'othered'.
Hex representation at different scales. Hex value is based on centroid's value.

tspan.tspan: Created by Cyrille Mdard de Chardon as part of #30DayMapChallenge (Day 4 - Hexagons). Projection: LUREF/Luxembourg (2169). Data source: CORINE Land Cover 2018 - EEA. Made with R and InkScape.
